@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fnilpm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.56 * wp.exp(v0))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.87)))
    tmp = tmp
    tmp = (wp.cos(0.13) + ((tmp + 0.69 * v0 + 0.29) + (v0 + 0.58 / tmp + 0.25)))
    v1 = 0.21
    v2 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.87) - 0.99) / 0.15)
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
